# SkillBridge Backend

## Project Overview

SkillBridge Backend is a scalable, secure, and production-ready RESTful API designed to power the complete SkillBridge tutor booking platform.

This backend manages the entire application workflow including authentication, authorization, tutor profile management, tutor availability scheduling, booking systems, review management, administrative controls, analytics, and platform moderation.

The platform is built to support a modern learning ecosystem where students can easily connect with tutors through a secure and structured session booking system.

SkillBridge focuses on creating a seamless experience for learners and educators by providing robust APIs for managing users, tutors, subjects, schedules, bookings, and reviews.

The system is designed with scalability, maintainability, and clean architecture principles in mind, making it suitable for real-world educational platforms and future feature expansion.

The platform supports three primary user roles:

### Student

Students can browse tutors, explore subjects, book tutoring sessions, manage their bookings, leave reviews, and maintain their personal profiles.

### Tutor

Tutors can create and manage tutor profiles, add teaching subjects, manage availability schedules, receive bookings, and monitor tutoring activities.

### Admin

Admins manage the entire platform including users, tutor verification, categories, subjects, featured tutors, platform analytics, and moderation tasks.

