# Roles & Permissions

| Role    | Description                         | Permissions                                                                 |
| ------- | ----------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Student | Learners who book tutoring sessions | Book sessions, manage bookings, leave reviews, update profile               |
| Tutor   | Experts who offer tutoring services | Create tutor profile, manage subjects, manage schedules, handle bookings    |
| Admin   | Platform moderators                 | Manage users, categories, tutors, analytics, bookings, and moderation tasks |

