# Base URL

```bash
http://localhost:5000
```

---

# Authentication

Authentication and session management are handled using **Better Auth**.

The authentication handler is mounted globally:

```ts
app.all("/api/auth/*splat", toNodeHandler(auth));
```

Protected routes use custom role-based authorization middleware.

Example:

```ts
auth(UserRoles.STUDENT, UserRoles.TUTOR, UserRoles.ADMIN);
```

This middleware ensures only authorized users can access protected resources based on their assigned roles.

